rivar en ataque a médicos y</span> <span style="color: black;font-size: 12pt;font-family: Times New Roman", serif;">enfermeros, es decir, en añadir más pesar a quienes forman el Ejército que nos está salvando… y que, naturalmente, acusa la fatiga.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:0cm;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n	https://storage.googleapis.com/medicina-responsable.appspot.com/1645457265875.jpg?GoogleAccessId=firebase-adminsdk-2sbvv%40medicina-responsable.iam.gserviceaccount.com&Expires=2524608000&Signature=nWWhn%2FJGbOrXw7nODjYeIo3iWz%2BTPc6Eo7RvWUBf7CRlkMYzPyLggsGoTfxa2aniOsFvYMDJn5wrhVrHiqhIXTGqGTpP0FYXXfJwTfSI5GPq92m7HcPkYZK5CE4xKJoxZqHz5BYNW%2FJAapZz0N4vy%2Bieh13D1Ricvj%2BvnGhAiKq%2F1fTG5oOXlmpFqLtLHLdFNTRvwq1sjbtO53SK9uwevlpBLM%2FGmD%2B9ZFyGvh7lxW7QlzNriEQVwWeMurKbBMuZhkMBox18u%2FjrNX5iRqA5OmPQFU1W%2BmQtqQrAni4B5GFf6SpswWuLOjhAp96%2BbfvlmtWgESAjz0TDzda4HaXQaQ%3D%3D	\N	\N	\N	https://youtu.be/Ggfka9gztQQ	https://storage.googleapis.com/medicina-responsable.appspot.com/1645457266977.jpg?GoogleAccessId=firebase-adminsdk-2sbvv%40medicina-responsable.iam.gserviceaccount.com&Expires=2524608000&Signature=vaRBVCQrUY6uTfUlRttOQ1bZYwHnSIRRbjIWMDR0VhMcq%2FIZ9VAUTsj0qciX%2FRxBCKqtJQg9I1NgHqb%2FQ6oBNRRQFy2CtYP8UsXXSFeACtFjCo5VFmn%2FBSjCB3hQQ3SCR61pHBF77TT6OI4v03WZxrJRJHf9yiR1r0uhLrGjckNmhwX2U93WjEtR2B1dvqz7Tq6hWjhELpw3dEOexiaeCtUVzVgmaTgMZz3bwe22Xtk6GK3xo81BCLY%2BrH%2FBKLxuqoBzW8cMxwWGlKTw6fbkutMizcMXeGcgUbwRg09H5qDmcn5zi%2FacTbOZVxMd%2BKcw%2B0xZfNF2g6INrldRLS78Rg%3D%3D	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	053c9b27-8acb-45f9-824d-aef610cac791	\N	\N	\N	PUBLISHED	2022-02-21 12:39:20.506	f	cca95dc0-1222-4610-8af8-1eecf5083952	fd625f70-1315-495b-94bd-e79afc1fa882	\N	\N	true	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N
